{"tid":1213332,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"星島日報係咪竟然報D咁野","createTime":"2019-06-13T01:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T01:29:38.000Z","uid":31927,"like":64,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"200defafe27751fbe5c3b38ef8222ed4e49e3db3","tid":1213332,"uid":31927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:19:55.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】《逃犯修訂》修訂引爆大規模警民衝突，特首林鄭月娥態度強硬，拒絕撤回修例。逾200名特首選舉委員會選委發表聲明，指6月9日有103萬市民遊行反對《逃犯條例》修訂，但林鄭依然漠視民意。昨天(12日)因政府的冷漠引發民眾自發佔領運動，但卻遭到警方暴力清場，比當年雨傘運動以更暴力方式對待示威者。<br />\n<br />\n聯署的選委認為林鄭已盡失其正當性，必須引咎下台，並重新改選新任特首。同時，有關的選委又要求警方立即停止暴力行為，撤回修例，還香港一個安全的法治社會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4295c27ebd1faaf5412ad072c22406c3eba5fea","tid":1213332,"uid":31927,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:20:51.000Z","msg":"星島日報竟然報D咁野<br />\nsor 打錯標題"},{"pid":"077569bd70312431b20c93d1b5a05acddbfa8192","tid":1213332,"uid":148332,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:21:31.000Z","msg":"果200個本身都唔係投比佢嫁啦...."},{"pid":"eda19a8efe11920f7d88ddd1cb8ef22db02bd759","tid":1213332,"uid":51105,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:22:40.000Z","msg":"個總編輯聽日唔洗返工"},{"pid":"c2efc437c2ee3f9564a921dbd55d509d6ba08f25","tid":1213332,"uid":62749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:23:53.000Z","msg":"星島大老闆都驚送中"},{"pid":"5821cdc229968f9c376d4086df3f188e5d69b467","tid":1213332,"uid":224429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:24:15.000Z","msg":"星島唔係維穩報黎?<br />\n換左人出?"},{"pid":"d390e118472c69f0f5ad7a2ca6d6fd3f59bc1b8e","tid":1213332,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:25:33.000Z","msg":"link? source?<br />\n頭版係話人暴動喎"},{"pid":"f8e77146166603e1c678683d58a16facaf2c7c99","tid":1213332,"